That would be absurd, and one at least of his own exemplos would contradict his theory, the jurisconsultus, who did not pursue his laborious vocation for pay. He therefore shifts or limite his ground a little, and dwells upon that which he supposes to be the most prevalent cause of discontent; and with his ground he changes his ex- amples.
